purpose: The email is a call for contributions to the SEWORLD mailing list, specifically inviting submissions related to the 18th IFIP WG8.1 Working Conference on the Practice of Enterprise Modeling. It also provides a link for more information about SEWORLD and its archives.
evidence_sentences: To contribute to SEWORLD, send your submission to mailto:[log in to unmask]
http://sigsoft.org/resources/seworld.html provides more information on SEWORLD as well as links to a complete archive of messages posted to the list.
